Package com.sun.darkstar.example.snowman.interfaces

Interface Summary
IComponent IComponent defines an interface for a Component which can be connected to other IComponent to form a bigger system.
IController IController defines the interface for all types of entity controller in the system which follows the MVC (Model View Controller) design pattern.
IDynamicView IDynamicView defines the interface for views that represent IDynamicEntity in the game world.
IGameState IGameState defines the interface for all types of game states that represent a particular stage of the game.
IInputConverter IInputConverter defines the interface for converters that converts jME input events to FengGUI events.
IRealTimeTask IRealTimeTask defines the interface for time dependent tasks.
ITask ITask defines the interface for all types of tasks that are generated in response to either user inputs received by various types of IController or packets processed by IProtocolProcessor.
